      "writtenOn": "2020-12-17T16:53:25Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yes, we do. Good catch. I\u0027m not sure how I did this - I seem to recall that the byte code generator had the same flaw (with an assert that there were no side effects in the two sides), but I see that\u0027s not true. So I don\u0027t know how I got here. Fixed.",
